articles.title: Thousands evacuated as India, Pakistan brace for Cyclone Biparjoy - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Classified as very severe cyclonic storm, Biparjoy is likely to make landfall on South Asian coasts on Thursday evening.
articles.content:
The coastal regions of India and Pakistan are on high alert with tens of thousands being evacuated a day before Cyclone Biparjoy is expected to make landfall.
